# Linear Triage - Issue Management

Triage Linear issues with inbox review, backlog management, and quick issue creation.

## Usage

```bash
# Review inbox (unassigned/untriaged) - default
/linear-triage

# Specific modes
/linear-triage inbox              # Untriaged issues
/linear-triage backlog            # All open issues
/linear-triage mine               # My assigned issues
/linear-triage update ENG-123     # Update specific issue
/linear-triage create "Title"     # Quick create

# Filters
/linear-triage --team Platform    # Specific team
/linear-triage --project "Hawk"   # Specific project
/linear-triage --priority urgent  # Priority filter
/linear-triage --label bug        # Label filter
```

