## Filters

| Filter | Description | Example |
|--------|-------------|---------|
| `--team` | Filter by team | `--team Platform` |
| `--project` | Filter by project | `--project Hawk` |
| `--priority` | Filter by priority | `--priority urgent` |
| `--label` | Filter by label | `--label bug` |
| `--assignee` | Filter by assignee | `--assignee @me` |
| `--limit N` | Max issues | `--limit 20` |

## Quick Keyboard Shortcuts (in interactive mode)

| Key | Action |
|-----|--------|
| `a` | Assign to me |
| `1-4` | Set priority |
| `d` | Mark as Done |
| `s` | Skip to next |
| `q` | Quit |

